
### [yabai](https://github.com/koekeishiya/yabai) - Tiling Window Manager

# 1. `yabai --start-service`
# 2. To reload config `yabai --restart-service`



# Space 1: Development
# Space 2: Browser
# Space 3: Other Applications

# See: https://github.com/koekeishiya/yabai/wiki/Configuration#configuration-file 
# `yabai --start-service`
# `yabai --restart-service`
yabai -m config --space 1 layout bsp
yabai -m config --space 2 layout bsp
yabai -m config --space 1 window_palcement second_child
yabai -m config --space 2 window_palcement second_child

yabai -m config top_padding    1
yabai -m config bottom_padding 1
yabai -m config left_padding   1
yabai -m config right_padding  1
yabai -m config window_gap     10 

# Disable yabai for macOS system apps
yabai -m rule --add app="^System Settings$" manage=off
yabai -m rule --add app="^Weather$" manage=off



# [JankyBorders](https://github.com/FelixKratz/JankyBorders)

#
# brew tap FelixKratz/formulae
# brew install borders
# yabai --restart-service
#
borders active_color=0xffe1e3e4 inactive_color=0xff494d64 width=5.0 &
